 Moreno said in a statement: “When we started working on &#39;Goodnight, God Bless, I Love U, Delete.&#39;, there was so much more light coming in my life, for numerous reasons.</p><p> “There&#39;s a lot more optimism. Even the darker themes are more romanticised and not coming from a place of despair.”</p><p> Watch the video for new single &#39;Invisible Hand&#39; and see the artwork and tracklist for &#39;Goodnight, God Bless, I Love U, Delete.&#39; below. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="††† (Crosses) - Invisible Hand (Official Music Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eiisOTm05W0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <strong>1. &#39;Pleasure&#39;<br /> 2. &#39;Invisible Hand&#39;<br /> 3. &#39;Found&#39;<br /> 4. &#39;Light As A Feather&#39;<br /> &#39;Pulseplagg&#39;<br /> &#39;Runner&#39;<br /> &#39;Big Youth&#39; (feat. El-P)<br /> &#39;End Youth&#39; (Reprise)<br /> &#39;Last Rites&#39;<br /> &#39;Ghost Ride&#39;<br /> &#39;Grace&#39;<br /> &#39;Eraser&#39;<br /> &#39;Natural Selection&#39;<br /> &#39;Girls Float † Boys Cry&#39; (feat. Robert Smith)<br /> &#39;Goodnight, God Bless, I Love U, Delete.&#39;</strong> </p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3478183" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover.jpeg" alt="十字架" width="1128" height="1128" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover.jpeg 1128w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-album-cover-696x696.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/crosses-